<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>In Zend_Db_Table_Row_Abstract @ rev.10042, line 807 :</p>

<p>$dependentTable = new $dependentTable(array('db' =&gt; $db));</p>

<p>For example, when you set a setRowClass or a setRowsetClass in the contructor $config parameter, the configuration is not merged with array('db' =&gt; $db). The array config is lost.</p>

<p>Result :
findDependentRowset() returns Zend_Db_Table_Abstract objects instead of myObject object.</p>

